channel.title: I downloaded the 461 client and got it working to real rs(video)
channel.description:
ok, i downloaded the 461 client from runescape and tested it.. first it stopped at connecting to update server.. as it done for most people
then i went around in like every .java file and got it working to connect to real rs and i even played alittle as you can see here on my video also with music....
now i know where it connects to.. so now i must learn to make it connect to my server... well all i can say Enjoy :P
took me like 2 hours to fix...
[url=http://youtube.com/watch?v=9-Gt5oVsyJc]http://youtube.com/watch?v=9-Gt5oVsyJc[/url] yay for working client
_______________-----------------------_______________----------------
what i typed there was low english
because this is my run client
[code]@echo off TITLE Kevinscape client set /p highlow=High or Low Memory Version[high or low]: set /p lang=Language[english or german]: java -Xmx500m client 119 live live %highlow%mem members %lang% game1 pause[/code]
